================================================================================
ATTRIBUTION AND ACKNOWLEDGMENTS:
================================================================================

Claudia Statusline is a complete Rust implementation of a statusline for 
Claude Code. While this is now an independent implementation, we acknowledge
and credit the original inspiration:

**Original Inspiration**: Peter Steinberger's statusline.rs gist
- Source: https://gist.github.com/steipete/8396e512171d31e934f0013e5651691e
- Author: Peter Steinberger (@steipete)
- The original gist provided the initial concept for a Claude Code statusline

**Current Implementation**: 
- This is a complete rewrite and enhancement in Rust
- Includes extensive features not present in the original:
  - Persistent statistics tracking with SQLite backend
  - Multi-console support with file locking
  - Security hardening with input validation
  - Progress bars and burn rate calculations
  - XDG compliance and atomic operations
  - Comprehensive test suite (79+ tests)
  - Cross-platform CI/CD automation

**Contributors**:
- See GitHub contributors list for all who have helped improve this project

This MIT License applies to the entire Claudia Statusline codebase as it exists
in this repository. We maintain proper attribution to acknowledge the original
inspiration while clarifying that this is now an independent work.